2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with large collections of artworks and uses self-supervised learning for feature adaptation. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with discovering near duplicate patterns in datasets. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses self-supervised learning for feature adaptation. 
5. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper deals with discovering patterns in art collections using machine learning techniques.
